    "Hence, the fine-tuning process should be adapted to the specific task requested and might not show similar performance levels for other tasks (e.g.",
    ": the model fine-tuned with the simple purpose of detecting purely AI generated text might show lower performance when detecting paraphrasing).",
    "Furthermore, the bias propensity of such AI tools must not be overlooked and should also be considered when applying these solutions.",
    "The approach here proposed will benefit from testing the results in much larger databases.",
    "This will improve the certainty that our proposed approach is reliable for larger sources of data."
